[
{The teddy bear remembers a birthday party of a seven year old. It was inside a large, colorful box.},
{The teddy bear remembers of a wonderful vacation with a child. Its name was Bearly.},
{The teddy bear recalls numerous nights with the child. The child was snuggled up in its arms.}
{The teddy bear thinks of the once child who is now fully grown. Somewhere beneath the dresser, moth balls are forming in its body.}
]

[
{$0 extends its arms, dragging #0 towards it. #0 chokes and thrashes, trying to free themselves.}
